{"tid":1101085,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"PUBG LITE","createTime":"2019-04-10T21:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T12:42:06.000Z","uid":213418,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b612db5f310668c6f7e44375e783c71e5129b5c7","tid":1101085,"uid":213418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T21:47:41.000Z","msg":"PUBG 繼在泰國開放《絕地求生 &ndash; 輕量版》PUBG Lite 公測後，港澳台地區也宣佈即將公測。開放公測時間定於3月28日 (星期四)，至於規格需求也同時公佈！官方聲稱「骨灰級的電腦都跑得動」，即文書筆電、老爺機都可以玩到輕量版的PUBG！<br />\n<br />\nPC版的PUBG是收費式的大逃殺類游戲，直到騰訊遊戲在手機上推出PUBG Mobile，讓內地及海外玩家都喜歡上了PUBG吃雞的樂趣。現在為了擴充市場，PUBG又在多地推出《絕地求生 &ndash; 輕量版》PUBG Lite，玩家可以免費進行與原版本相同的遊戲體驗。而在公開測試期間，遊戲內更會提供經典的 Erangel 、 Miramar 地圖，以及訓練模式供玩家選擇。<br />\n<br />\n3月28日 港澳台 PUBG Lite 公測：<a href=\"https://lite.pubg.com/download/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flite.pubg.com%2Fdownload%2F&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUj6T6zfZKY9%2BYzH6xvUt7sk%3D&h=7eb6bae3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lite.pubg.com/download/</a><br />\n<br />\n至於最低規格連 Intel HD Graphics 4000 的內顯都玩到，雖然比不上難無規格要求的PC模擬器PUBG Mobile版，但對於 PC 玩家而言又是一刺激遊戲！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U21eOa2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU21eOa2.png&h=a1e09c89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qe6p1o8mIkA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fqe6p1o8mIkA&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUj6T6zfZKY9%2BYzH6xvUt7sk%3D&h=07470dab\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qe6p1o8mIkA</a><br />\n<br />\n雖然畫質同效果一定唔及steam版pubg 但係免費嚟講我覺得都還可以 有巴絲玩緊可以一齊分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e7c48418b4bbf443d1da4152df0fd647ac0c52","tid":1101085,"uid":180469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T21:53:20.000Z","msg":"咁係咪用mac就玩唔到啦？"},{"pid":"0321110d863f8e90aaf9620d72715f1639f6ec9c","tid":1101085,"uid":103497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0